    dc:description "Figure 7. Female of Dysdera nakhchivanica, endogyne, dorsal. Abbreviations: Da - dorsal arch, Pd - posterior diverticulum, Re - receptacle, Rl - receptacular lateral edge, Tb - transverse bar. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." ;
